data.description: Welcome to this newly renovated ranch boasting seamless blend of modern upgrades and spacious comfort! Step inside to discover large airy rooms to include brand new flooring throughout entire home almost 2900 sq ft! The newly renovated interior includes an additional 4th bedroom.  This home has ample space for family and guests.  Enjoy the ease of multiple living areas, complemented by upgraded lighting fixtures that create the perfect ambiance for any occasion. The chef's dream kitchen offers top of the line appliances and ample counter space with a custom drop down butcher block cutting board.  Don't miss the luxury primary bathroom remodel with spa like dual shower heads, luxury lighting and tile design choices.  Outside, the newly upgrade backyard features rock accents and artificial grass section perfect for outdoor gathering or relaxation.  Park at ease with the 3 car garage and stay cool with the new split AC system.  This is comfort and style at an affordable price!
